# FactoryWaste Copilot - environment example
#
# The demo runs fully offline with NO key. The deterministic mock narrator is
# the default and needs nothing here.
#
# A key is only needed if you want Claude to phrase the (already grounded)
# answers instead of the built-in template narrator. In this static demo the
# key is entered at runtime in the Settings panel and kept in memory only.
# This file documents the variable name for a server-side deployment variant.

# Optional. If you wire up a server-side narration route, read the key from here.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Optional model override (defaults to claude-3-5-haiku-latest).
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-3-5-haiku-latest
